 This is an auto-grader page.

9
00:00:30,920 --> 00:00:35,880
 So you'll notice it has the instructions for that assignment that you just completed, right?

10
00:00:35,880 --> 00:00:39,420
 So you go to the auto-grader, it usually tells you where the instructions are.

11
